   WINDOWS (TM) ICON

        . We've included an icon to be used with Microsoft Windows.  The
          filename is DAEMON.ICO and can be associated with the program
          through the properties window.

   TRIVIA SCREEN

        . Users have asked for the TOTAL PURCHASE DOLLARS and the TOTAL SALES
          DOLLARS to reflect the individual prices multiplied times the
          quantity of cards.  Two new tally fields have been added to the
          Trivia screen, appearing next to TOTAL PURCHASE DOLLARS and TOTAL
          SALES DOLLARS respectively.

